lead_paragraph: The Wells Fargo Championship deleted a photo posted on its official Twitter account of fans wearing sombreros and fake mustaches to celebrate Cinco de Mayo after it was deemed insensitive.

headline.print_headline: Golf Tournament Removes 'Insensitive' Tweet on Cinco De Mayo
